title: Cassi with Belt AND Boots???

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body:
So I was looking at one of my friend's match history to see the last time he played. I found something very interesting...

2016 is MYMU
Explain this please.

replies.body:
The game was played back when Cassiopeia could buy boots.

EDIT: Oh, are you talking about the hextech protobelt? Yeah, when new items get introduced and old items get taken out, sometimes the icons for the new items will replace the icons for the old ones when looking at past matches.
I just thought about it and realized Protobelt could've actually replaced Will of The Ancients, since that is the only thing that would seem to make sense.
Possibly a glitch in the champion or item icon.
